# Prufs

**The decision trail for AI-generated code.**

Prufs captures the full chain of reasoning behind every line of AI-generated code - from human directive through agent interpretation, decision alternatives, constraints, and implementation - as a queryable causal graph.

Git tracks *what* changed. Prufs tracks *why*.

## Architecture

```
SDK (TypeScript)          Captures decision trail events from AI coding agents
    |
    v
Ingestion Service         Receives events via HTTP, writes to graph store
    |
    v
Neo4j Graph Store         Stores the causal decision graph
    |
    v
Trail API (GraphQL)       Unified query layer for trail traversal
    |
    +---> VS Code Extension    Hover-to-trail in the editor
    +---> Trail Visualizer     Interactive web UI for exploring trails
```

## Quick Start

### 1. Start the graph store

```bash
cd docker && docker compose up -d neo4j
```

### 2. Install dependencies and build

```bash
npm install
cd packages/sdk && npm run build
cd ../ingestion && npm run build
```

### 3. Run the demo

```bash
npx tsx scripts/demo-trail.ts
```

### 4. Start the ingestion service (requires Neo4j)

```bash
cd packages/ingestion && npm run start
```

## SDK Usage

```typescript
import { TrailRecorder } from "@prufs/sdk";

const trail = new TrailRecorder({
  project_id: "my-project",
  transport: "local", // or "http://localhost:3100"
  agent_id: "claude-code",
  model_id: "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
});

await trail.startSession();

// Record the human's directive
const d = await trail.directive("Add user search to admin panel");

// Record the agent's interpretation
const i = await trail.interpretation(d, "Implement search endpoint...", {
  confidence: 0.9,
});

// Record a decision with alternatives
const dec = await trail.decision(i, {
  chosen: "Elasticsearch",
  alternatives: [
    {
      description: "PostgreSQL FTS",
      rejection_reason: "No existing index",
    },
  ],
  rationale: "ES index already exists, supports fuzzy matching",
  domain_tags: ["search", "database"],
});

// Record the implementation
const impl = await trail.implementation([dec], {
  file_changes: [
    { path: "src/search.ts", change_type: "added", lines_added: 120, lines_removed: 0 },
  ],
  commit_sha: "abc123",
});

await trail.endSession();
```

## Project Structure

```
prufs/
  packages/
    sdk/           TypeScript capture SDK (npm package)
    ingestion/     Event ingestion service (Fastify + Neo4j)
    trail-api/     GraphQL API (Phase 3)
    linker/        Code-graph linker (Phase 3, Rust + Tree-sitter)
    visualizer/    Trail visualizer web UI (Phase 4)
  docker/          Docker Compose for local development
  scripts/         Demo and utility scripts
```

## Status

Phase 1 (Weeks 1 - 3): Graph foundation + SDK skeleton - **In Progress**

